item.description:
Tickets are $15 cash only at the door - if you mention Linda from Meetup.

Admission to the comedy show also includes the dance party afterwards!

Purchase advance tickets by calling 1-800-71 LAUGH or by e-mailing frankscomedysafari@yahoo.com.


Frank's Comedy Safari!- is a Comedy Show in Worcester. It is located at 90 Commercial Street in Worcester. The 5th Amendment Restaurant is at the corner of Commercial Street and Martin Luther King Boulevard. Food is available before and during the show! The show starts Saturday night at 9 pm, so let's get there at 8:00-8:30 pm to eat and get our seats. They advertise that they hire the best comics from Boston, New York and all over the New England Area.

Tickets can be purchased by calling 1-800-71 LAUGH or by e-mailing frankscomedysafari@yahoo.com.
item.how_to_find_us: We can meet inside prior to getting our seats
